{"tid":1422444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】民間記招可以搞，但係要有技巧","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:34:30.000Z","uid":277550,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de209313b3cb77adff08f524f5f1d63698f2342f","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"首先多謝巴絲打努力！作為老鬼一名，只希望留低少少原則性建議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一，提防騎劫</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n前因唔再討論。閣下認為有左膠陰謀又好，豬隊友又好，其實係冇分別！反正都係同一個後果。而呢個後果有幾毀滅性，以史為鑑，唔使我多講。<br />\n<br />\n所以，出鏡嘅手足要做到四件事：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1, 要完全遮面，包括眼睛。<br />\n2, 要承諾不接納任何單獨采訪。<br />\n3, 不能透露任何形式嘅身份，         包括網名，account等。<br />\n4, 要不時換人。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二，切忌有意或無意地發出「談判」訊號</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如能做到第一項，已經消除咗一大半談判嘅可能性，但要做得切底，就要有三項基本認知：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1, 我哋一坐低傾，就係重新賦予政權憲制，法律，及道德上嘅合法性。<br />\n<br />\n2, 未有任何實質戰功之前嘅談判叫「勸降」，唔係「議和」。<br />\n<br />\n3, 其實佢一個記招，然後我哋轉頭又一個記招回應，已經係某程度上嘅對話，請緊記！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n歡迎開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港！"},{"pid":"4e30bf6298ae947afc402281bbfd26f43062ecd0","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8abb07c5e6c3c72dac81fee95f0db7c9340dc4c9","tid":1422444,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe12390e10edca9110e4c410334d9918d05579ce","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c76c07301068f9f25ddb8952244f8260d5c5a4d","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"ef28f3819a9a5e7ab8edc160bdb1fa3faa4e3761","tid":1422444,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"297643aeb8a8ec2c2222f4c1b5b183599f36fdfa","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"881b41705ba20bfe4990db6f8f49a1759f68e36b","tid":1422444,"uid":176657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"一定要包實d 唔想手足比人點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a14b539665357ee76b13cfe73c3d291e523f4c3","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"881b41705ba20bfe4990db6f8f49a1759f68e36b","tid":1422444,"uid":176657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"一定要包實d 唔想手足比人點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"甚至係俾有心人擺上枱。。。"},{"pid":"e6d1366534bb0d8e025bbfa19552ba76603a1e07","tid":1422444,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"天佑香港 反官警黑勾結"},{"pid":"5ac5d5034e6f8a3e1e129fe7a48766adb735786a","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"自推x3"},{"pid":"50d8cdc3bf72efa5b7b3940c4f0e7bd1cdb35331","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"自推x4"},{"pid":"794e7aa5b5f3951028a461be10fbe42493889975","tid":1422444,"uid":277550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"自推x5"},{"pid":"d400e6cca3d2a341e81250aca2ba59c86607d4